quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  37,154,"Ko he…ìi on, onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, hi…óon √±aawira ndee √±aaaworaa oo√±iinde, wa…óanon Alla …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, su…ìao…óon hoore-mon wor…ìe …ìen?"
  37,155,"E on miijitotaako wonnde ko e meere won…óon e mun? Tawde si on taskike, on yi'iray non bonnde fi…ìnde mon nden."
  37,156,"Kaa hi…óon jogii hujja e dalil …ìanngir…óo Deftere maa Nulaa…óo?"
  37,157,"Haray addee deftere mon ka hujja mon on woni …óon, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe e haala!"
  37,158,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen wa…ói hakkunde Allah e Malaa'ika'en, asko dammbe, …óum ko ko …ìe aa∆¥inoo wonnde Malaa'ika'en, ko …ìi…ó…ìe Allah rew…ìe! Hara non, …ìen Malaa'ikaa…ìe no anndi, pellet, Alla tawnoyay …ìen sirkoo…ìe, e hasboore nden."
  37,159,"Allah senike O laa…ìii, gaay e kon sirkoo…ìe …ìen sifotoo, dammbude Mo …ìi…ó…óo e genndiraawo, ekw immorde e ka yahdaa e Makko!"
  37,160,"Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Allah, la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen. ∆Åen …óon sifortaa Allah, ko yahdaani e Makko."
  37,161,"Anndon onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, e ko rewoton kon gaanin Allah."
  37,162,"On wonaali majjiniroo…ìe kon ko rewoton, wo…ó…ìe goo e diine goonga."
  37,163,"Si wanaa on mo Allah winndani naatugol ka Yiite. On …óon yeddiray sa…ìu …óum, o naata nge. Onon non, e rewetee…ói mon …óin, on alaa nden feere."
  37,164,"Malaa'ika'en …ìanngini jeyeede ma…ì…ìe ka Allah, da…óndinoo e ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen aa∆¥ori…ìe kon, wi'ugol: Alaa e amen, mo alanaa …óum, darorde anndaande, fii rewugol Alla …óoftoo Mo."
  37,165,"Menen Malaa'ika, ko men darnaa…ìe saffinaa, fii rewugol Allah …óoftoo Mo. Ko memen kadi woni subbunhinantoo…ìe Allah …ìen, sifaaji yahdu…ói e Makko."
  37,166,"Menen Malaa'ika, ko men darnaa…ìe saffinaa, fii rewugol Allah …óoftoo Mo. Ko memen kadi woni seninoo…ìe Allah ko O haandaani ko sifaaji."
  37,167,"Sirkoo…ìe Makkah …ìen woniino e wi'ugol, ado nuleede Muhammadu (yo o his): Sinno hara me…óen joginoo Deftere sugu Defte arane …óen, wano Tawreeta, ko pellet, men la…ì…ìinanayno Alla dewalngal. Hara non, ko e fenaande …ìe woni. Tawde Muhammadu addanii …ìe Alqur'aana, …ìe yeddi nde. Kono non, aray nde …ìe anndata, fii lepte sa…ótu…óe, ha…ì…ìii…óe …ìe …óen, √ëalnde Darngal."
  37,168,""
  37,169,""
  37,170,""
  37,171,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, wonnde ko …ìe wallirtee…ìe e hoore ay…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ìe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ìirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ìamtora."
  37,172,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, wonnde pellet, ko …ìe wallirtee…ìe e hoore ay…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ìe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ìirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ìamtora."
  37,173,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, wonnde ko …ìe wallirtee…ìe e hoore ay…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, hujja e dolle …óe Alla neeminiri …ìe. E wonnde poolal ngal, ko fii konu Amen, ha…ìirayngu fii Alla ngun, no daalol Alla ngol …ìamtora."
  37,174,"An Nulaa…óo, …óuurno …ìee sirkoo…ìe sa…óta feeree…ìe, haa e saanga nde Allah humpitu maa, arugol lepte ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  37,175,"Ndaaraa …ìe, tuma lepte …óen jippotoo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe aray yi'ude, ka yi'ugol nafataa …ìe!"
  37,176,"E hara ko lepte Alla …óen, …ìee sirkoo…ìe he√±orta?"
  37,177,"Si lepte Allah …óen jippike e ma…ì…ìe, haray bimmbi ma…ì…ìe on bonii !"
  37,178,"An Nulaa…óo, …óuurno e ma…ì…ìe, haa Allah √±aawa fii leptugol …ìe ngol."
  37,179,"Ndaaraa; kam…ìe kadi, …ìe aray yi'ude lepte Allah …óen yanooje e ma…ì…ìe."
  37,180,"Senayee woodanii Joomi maa, an Muhammadu, O laa…ìii e kon ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen siforta Mo e ustii…ói !"
  37,181,"Kisiyee Allah e mantoore Makko, wonii e Nulaa…ìe Makko teddu…ìe …ìen."
  37,182,"Yettoore nden fow, woodanii Alla senii…óo toowu…óo On. Ko Kanko hanndi e …óum. Ko Kanko woni Jey…óo winndere nden fow. Jey…óo …óum alaa, si wanaa Kanko."